latestPosts.caption:
Hello everyone! I started this account a little more than a year ago and want to properly introduce myself to all those that have followed along on this journey with me and those that are new here. Welcome to my page!

I am a Mom of 2 boys and I have always loved fashion. I’ve always been a girly girl and love all the fancy things. On my page you will find a mix of affordable finds and investment pieces- whether that’s for casual wear, athletic clothes, or dressy styles. I love trying new trends, but also wearing classic staples that can be styled year after year. I often stick to neutral tones and you will see those colors form the base for most of my looks. 

If you connect with any of that- then you are in the right place! And I’m so happy you are here! I cannot wait to share more style inspo with you 🖤

I post all of my outfits on LTK. You can shop these looks here: https://liketk.it/4TWNj
